scenes.description: Promotional screen for the 'Sinderella' vinyl release.
Infomercial parody 'Shop Till You Drop Dead' for Mori Calliope's birthday merchandise.
Live concert teaser for 'New Underworld Order' major debut concert.
Merchandise and Blu-ray purchase benefits info screens with background music.
Looping restart of the 'Shop Till You Drop Dead' commercial segment.

subtitles.original:
Mori Calliope Sinderella
2023.06.07 Vinyl Release!!
subtitles.english:
Mori Calliope Sinderella
2023.06.07 Vinyl Release!!

subtitles.original: Tired of owning useless items you'll never use...
subtitles.english: Tired of owning useless items you'll never use...

subtitles.original: ...because you got lured in by that low, low price of 19.99?
subtitles.english: ...because you got lured in by that low, low price of 19.99?

subtitles.original: Well, fear not!
subtitles.english: Well, fear not!

subtitles.original: Because on today's shopping program, Shop Till You Drop Dead...
subtitles.english: Because on today's shopping program, Shop Till You Drop Dead...

subtitles.original: ...featuring Calliope Mori.
subtitles.english: ...featuring Calliope Mori.

subtitles.original: None of our items are 19.99!
subtitles.english: None of our items are 19.99!

subtitles.original: Haha! Oh no!
subtitles.english: Haha! Oh no!

subtitles.original: Get ready to feast your eyes on some premium tier items...
subtitles.english: Get ready to feast your eyes on some premium tier items...

subtitles.original: ...you'll literally want to gouge your eyes out...
subtitles.english: ...you'll literally want to gouge your eyes out...

subtitles.original: ...if you don't own them out of sheer FOMO...
subtitles.english: ...if you don't own them out of sheer FOMO...

subtitles.original: ...and additional existential dread of the emptiness of your life without them.
subtitles.english: ...and additional existential dread of the emptiness of your life without them.

subtitles.original: You need these items.
subtitles.english: You need these items.

subtitles.original: You need them!
subtitles.english: You need them!

subtitles.original: Why not get a sick poster of your one and only boy...
subtitles.english: Why not get a sick poster of your one and only boy...

subtitles.original: ...to display at work and assert your dominance over your friends?
subtitles.english: ...to display at work and assert your dominance over your friends?

subtitles.original: That's right folks, Mori Calliope's special birthday poster...
subtitles.english: That's right folks, Mori Calliope's special birthday poster...

subtitles.original: ...features Mori Calliope rocking out at a concert she definitely did...
subtitles.english: ...features Mori Calliope rocking out at a concert she definitely did...

subtitles.original: ...with an outfit she definitely wore!
subtitles.english: ...with an outfit she definitely wore!

subtitles.original: You won't want to miss this premium item...
subtitles.english: You won't want to miss this premium item...

subtitles.original: ...'cause once it's gone, it's gone for good.
subtitles.english: ...'cause once it's gone, it's gone for good.

subtitles.original: Fuck you scalpers, get it now!
subtitles.english: Fuck you scalpers, get it now!

subtitles.english: Ever wanted to bathe yourself in sweet smelling, delicious purple liquid?

subtitles.english: But if you do, then you better get your hands...

subtitles.original: ...on this special dual set of bath bombs...
subtitles.english: ...on this special dual set of bath bombs...

subtitles.original: ...from Mori Calliope's favorite premium Underworld Onsen.

subtitles.english: They come in two scents:

subtitles.english: Mori Rose and Death-sensei Purple Mist.

subtitles.english: Your Mori dad!
